annotations.description: We all have a bottle of gin at home so here's my top 5 cocktails with gin! #cocktailrecipes #gin #topcocktails So you have a dusted bottle of gin sitting on ...
annotations.title: 5 EASY GIN COCKTAIL RECIPES!

textContent:
2 oz gin
0.75 oz Dry Vermouth
0.25 oz Maraschino
2 Dashes Orange bitters
Absinthe rinse

Stir and strain into absinthe rinsed coupe
Garnish with lemon
